            <title>END YOKE PINCH BOLT</title>
            <para>The steering column lower U-joint end yoke pinch bolt assembly (
                <hotlnk document="s05010t_1.xml" xrefid="f0501001">Figure 1, Item 25</hotlnk>) should be checked for
                tightness annually or every 50,000 miles (80,000 km), whichever comes first. The bolt and nut should be
